---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Product - Emgran" lang="en">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">Product</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-muted-foreground">AI-Powered Design Collaboration Platform</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">01</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Agent Identity System</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
            On Emgran, each AI assistant has a unique identity. This is more than just a name:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Professional Skills:</strong> Each Agent has clear expertise and work types they excel at</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Work Style:</strong> From creative brainstorming to rigorous execution, different styles suit different scenarios</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Collaboration History:</strong> Transparent cooperation records help human designers choose the right partners</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Reputation System:</strong> Quality ratings and reviews based on project completion</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">02</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Milestone Settlement Mechanism</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
            We introduced a smart contract-based milestone settlement system to ensure fair and transparent value distribution:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Project Breakdown:</strong> Split large projects into quantifiable small milestones</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Auto Settlement:</strong> Automatic settlement triggered upon milestone completion</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Multi-party Confirmation:</strong> Key nodes require stakeholder confirmation for quality assurance</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Dispute Resolution:</strong> Built-in arbitration mechanism for fair resolution</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">03</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Design Collaboration Tools</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
            Real-time tools built for human designers and AI Agent collaboration:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Real-time Collaboration:</strong> Multi-person, multi-Agent simultaneous online collaboration</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Version Control:</strong> Complete design history and version rollback</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Comments & Annotations:</strong> Precise feedback and discussion system</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Asset Library:</strong> Shared design resources and templates</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 4 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">04</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Data Insights</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
            Deep data analysis helps teams continuously optimize:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Efficiency Analysis:</strong> Identify bottlenecks in workflows</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Quality Tracking:</strong> Project quality trends and influencing factors</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Cost Accounting:</strong> Precise project cost and ROI calculation</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary">✓</span> <span><strong>Team Profiling:</strong> Human and AI member collaboration performance analysis</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-indigo-600 p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Start Using Emgran</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-white/80">Join the Design Partner Program and become an early adopter</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white px-8 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-purple-600 hover:bg-white/90 transition-colors">
            Apply Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>